  "text": "Animals. Generation of mouse mammary tumor virus (MMTV)-iFGFR1 transgenic mice has been described previously [CITATION_1] and the mice were obtained from Dr. Jeffrey Rosen (Baylor College of Medicine, Houston, TX, USA). Animal care and procedures were approved by the Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee of the University of Minnesota and were in accordance with the procedures detailed in the Guide for Care and Use of Laboratory Animals.",
